---
title: Vietnamese Caramelised Pork Bowl with Garlic Rice, Rainbow Slaw & Fried Egg
description: This bountiful bowl has "new favourite" written all over it! The oyster sauce is the key ingredient, giving a delicious flavour kick
to the mince. With tender rainbow veggies, garlic rice and a fried egg to top things off, it's a winner from start to finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chinese-style-pork-bowl-cfa99d86.jpg
